{"tid":978220,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"《認真》點辟豬屎味","createTime":"2019-01-11T17:37:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-11T22:18:31.000Z","uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4c71bc7ec73cc39f923fe20a03efa5f5900d29bd","tid":978220,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T17:37:37.000Z","msg":"屋企住村屋，外邊方圓唔知幾多里有農場，有豬有羊有雞<br />\n<br />\n日頭都好地地<br />\n一到夜晚無太陽就臭到仆街<br />\n陣陣豬屎味 <br />\n<br />\n奈何個廳無窗<br />\n一定要開露台個門，唔開就焗到仆街又唔想0徒錢開冷氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夜晚真係好難頂<br />\n<br />\n各位大佬有無咩方法解決？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8fe61c3ab8642c40862c0f45b4382daaf54fafd","tid":978220,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T18:39:15.000Z","msg":"戴口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9a2d9ccaf987b3d3d635a46b7280bbed083e173","tid":978220,"uid":131278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T18:44:15.000Z","msg":"點香抗衡得唔得呀？"},{"pid":"6c2dfcad87c5f5a6292b988dead9b987bb32c8b4","tid":978220,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T19:34:53.000Z","msg":"嗅覺係會習慣<br />\n<br />\n公司有放香薰，d客黎到都話好香，但我就完全唔覺有味"},{"pid":"5a61337ab0e4c9883d9d4129e518d586bf414777","tid":978220,"uid":193476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T19:44:25.000Z","msg":"應該開冷氣都會臭，無得搞，成個環境空氣都係豬豬咪，頂唔到就唯有搬啦。"},{"pid":"d8cb77e51c6833ddc81cbe079039d3ac921e43a4","tid":978220,"uid":183219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T19:46:10.000Z","msg":"空氣清新機"},{"pid":"1367a4d3d8fa37cf15ec8faac6d82b9ab5d9a1fb","tid":978220,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8fe61c3ab8642c40862c0f45b4382daaf54fafd","tid":978220,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"