e":"2019-01-11T20:33:49.000Z","msg":"唯有食多啲豬羊雞補數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0ab5836cdb960494b96c182849b49c47cc74248","tid":978220,"uid":2110,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ec14751ab997bdd5332d6596d9b41399acc3395","tid":978220,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c5093f51b24c79587be5025318932eabf90975c","tid":978220,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9b51304f6824a1d388a61e46263e065bbe5d863","tid":978220,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T20:30:09.000Z","msg":"所以唯有等到變習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nD味由外面黎，你解決唔到源頭好難做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T20:31:11.000Z","msg":"真係唔掂，呢幾日陣味真係好勁，女人聞左20分鐘度就呂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T20:31:37.000Z","msg":"嘔呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T21:18:01.000Z","msg":"幫你查左小小資料，試下打去環保署投訴<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.epd.gov.hk/epd/tc_chi/how_help/report_pollution/csc_more.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epd.gov.hk%2Fepd%2Ftc_chi%2Fhow_help%2Freport_pollution%2Fcsc_more.html&d=yYlPmL2gj%2Fdded%2FW4V25Im6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=e74eef9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.epd.gov.hk/epd/tc_chi/how_help/report_pollution/csc_more.html</a><br />\n<br />\n市民可致電本顧客服務中心，舉報環境污染問題。<br />\n<br />\n一般的污染投訴包括如下︰<br />\n<br />\n不適當處理建築廢物<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">異味惡臭，煙霧及其他空氣污染物滋擾</span><br />\n工業商業的噪音滋擾及在限制時間內的建築噪音<br />\n非法排放污水<br />\n不適當處理化學或禽畜廢物<br />\n不適當處理電子廢物<br />\n光滋擾<br />\n其他污染問題<br />\n當收到有關污染投訴後，本署職員會盡快跟進，務求令市民的投訴得到妥善處理。"},{"pid":"272d929e26629eaaec40a11fe10cf504ebe7de76","tid":978220,"uid":166040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T22:01:08.000Z","msg":"你傳d非洲豬瘟過去咪好快冇哂豬囉"},{"pid":"5e9cb1f1a3f3d63ec53b308d2463de27c2ebc950","tid":978220,"uid":201768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score